{
  "text": "All patients had follow-up appointments after an average period of 15.8\u00b13.8 months (6~24 months) for the PPSF group and 14.6\u00b15.4 months (6~24 months) for the MWPSF group, with no statistically significant difference between the two groups (p=0. [CITATION_1] . No significant differences existed between the two groups in terms of age, sex, body mass index (BMI), and disease duration. Ninety-seven patients who achieved bone union prior to the final follow-up underwent a second operation to remove the implants.",
